re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鑄造定打造呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鑄造同打造係唔同技術，打係加熱金屬再打到變形，鑄係要溶咗d金屬倒入模內冷卻，打造武器唔可以話錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 有睇it will kill</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刀呢啲係鍛造 所以先有鍛煉呢個詞語<br />\n唔會有人講 打造 最多話 打鐵<br />\n<br />\n所以：打你老母造咩 用埋啲匪話蝗語"},{"pid":"1435dcd74db9f7cd6de27e25da68b570c6925941","tid":33002,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>刀你老母牙😤😤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2ce96577160473630246d98f0d84790a17a352","tid":33002,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鑄造定打造呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鑄造同打造係唔同技術，打係加熱金屬再打到變形，鑄係要溶咗d金屬倒入模內冷卻，打造武器唔可以話錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 有睇it will kill</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刀呢啲係鍛造 所以先有鍛煉呢個詞語<br />\n唔會有人講 打造 最多話 打鐵<br />\n<br />\n所以：打你老母造咩 用埋啲匪話蝗語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宋 吳自牧 《夢粱錄&middot;嫁娶》：&ldquo;若富家官戶，多用金銀打造魚筯各一雙。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n《水滸傳》第五六回：&ldquo;小可是祖傳打造軍器為生&hellip;&hellip;若要打造，便可下手。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n魯迅 《花邊文學&middot;刀&ldquo;式&rdquo;辯》：&ldquo;這或者也難怪，不是 日本 人，怎么會掛&lsquo; 日本 指揮刀&rsquo;呢？一定是照 日本 式樣，自己打造的了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n中文有好多同義詞嘅，鍛造係啱，係咪唔代表打造就錯呢？用打嘅方法造出一樣物件咪打造囉。<br />\n<br />\n至於咩打造品牌乜乜，樣嘢都唔關打事所以咪錯囉。唔洗反到蝗語用過嘅字就唔用嘅，用係啱嘅地方就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcff8657a6df8eee4fd4d9dfb091295a7355c3ec","tid":33002,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鑄造定打造呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鑄造同打造係唔同技術，打係加熱金屬再打到變形，鑄係要溶咗d金屬倒入模內冷卻，打造武器唔可以話錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 有睇it will kill</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刀呢啲係鍛造 所以先有鍛煉呢個詞語<br />\n唔會有人講 打造 最多話 打鐵<br />\n<br />\n所以：打你老母造咩 用埋啲匪話蝗語</blockquote><br />\n你都戇撚鳩 文盲就去讀多啲書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}